Hi, In case you have gotten any &quot;traditional&quot; evp (just a voice recorder
used), have you ever tried to listen directly through a external mic
connected to an &quot;line in&quot; input in any voice recorder device or mp3 (iriver
ifp for example).



I believe maybe it would be possible to listen directly  that kind of evp
while recording, and maybe will not be necessary to wait until the recording
is finished and playback it.





I would like to know your experience in case you got it.





Regards



Gustavo 












